Abandon Ship is the debut studio album from Australian electro house duo Knife Party. It is due for release on 24 November 2014 after being postponed from the 27 October 2014 and is to be released by Earstorm Records and Big Beat Records. However, on the 7th of November 2014, the iTunes Store released the album early, and has been acknowledged by Knife Party themselves.
